    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements matrix. The model is accepted as fit for the purpose of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device in support of pre-market submission.",
